    is_subset.Rd

    Subset Interstroke and keep case/control match

    Usage

    is_subset(interstroke_data, subset_rule)

    Arguments

    interstroke_data

    An Interstroke Dataset

    subset_rule

    A subsetting rule e.g. "age <= 45"

    Value

    An Interstroke Dataset

    Examples

    is_subset(interstroke_data = interstroke_stress, subset_rule = eage <= 45)
